<<<<<System requirements>>>>> Before running this container, ensure your system meets the following requirements.

        Apptainer / Singularity runtime
        Linux x86_64 architecture

        NVIDIA GPU with CUDA support (required for practical serving; a
        CPU-only node will only pass the container's basic import check)
        NVIDIA Container Toolkit for GPU access
        CUDA-compatible GPU driver

        RAM and disk requirements scale with the model being served — plan
        for enough free disk space to hold the model weights (and the
        Hugging Face cache, if downloading), and enough RAM/VRAM headroom
        for the chosen tensor-parallel configuration

        For multi-node serving: a fast interconnect (InfiniBand recommended,
        Ethernet supported) between nodes participating in the Ray cluster

<<<<</System requirements>>>>>
