<<<<<Included Packages>>>>> The container ships with a complete LLM inference stack pre-installed, so serving works out of the box with no extra setup. This is a representative list of the core packages present across builds of this container family, not the full install — run a shell inside the container and use `pip list` to see everything actually installed in a given build.

        Core Inference Stack
        --------------------------------
        vllm, torch, torchvision, torchaudio, ray

        Model & Tokenization
        --------------------------------
        transformers, tokenizers, huggingface_hub, safetensors,
        sentencepiece, accelerate

        API Server
        --------------------------------
        fastapi, uvicorn, pydantic, openai

        Supporting Libraries
        --------------------------------
        numpy, bitsandbytes, opencv-python-headless

