<<<<<Directory Structure>>>>> These paths exist inside the container — bind your own folders onto them so the container can read your model weights and use scratch space:

        /model           model weights (bind your own) + hf-cache/ for
                         auto-downloaded Hugging Face Hub models
        /scratch         node-local scratch space (temp files, not kept)
        /code            not used by this container (reserved, house convention)
        /data            not used by this container (reserved, house convention)
        /output          not used by this container (reserved, house convention)

        Also automatically available, no --bind needed:
        $HOME            your normal home directory
        /tmp             temp space

<<<<</Directory Structure>>>>>
